     特别注意用于遵从<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextOffset%2A>，<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextLength%2A>上原始<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>创建时<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A>对新<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>实例。  
  
